                            <div id="gts-content-2" class="accordion__content">
                                <p data-block-key="imjv4">A frequent rail service operates between London Paddington and St Ives via Reading, Exeter, Plymouth, Bodmin, Truro, St Erth and Penzance. A local train service operates from St Erth to St Ives. For train times and booking see:</p><p data-block-key="c850d"><a href="http://www.nationalrail.co.uk/">National Rail Enquiries</a> or call 08457 000 125 <a href="https://www.gwr.com/">Great Western Railway</a></p>
